response.overview: They're beautiful, talented and sexy. They came from all over the country to complete. But only one can be the next Raw Diva and win a $250,000 WWE contract. Relive the excitement, from the initial contestant selection to the challenges, eliminations and special events, including the Diva dodgeball game from SummerSlam 2004. From top to bottom, this year's hottest competition reveals the making of a $250,000 Raw Diva Search winner!
response.title: WWE $250,000 Raw Diva Search
